$ Perl module Text::Diff::FormattedHTML

`Text::Diff::FormattedHTML` creates a *side by side* → development/web/HTML/tags/table[HTML table] diff of two files.

Colors can (should) be adjusted through → development/web/CSS.

{ script.pl

  gh|PerlModules|/Text/Diff/FormattedHTML/script.pl||

}
{ one.txt

  gh|PerlModules|/Text/Diff/FormattedHTML/one.txt||

}
{ two.txt

  gh|PerlModules|/Text/Diff/FormattedHTML/two.txt||

}
{ Result

  The script generates this table:
  → development/languages/Perl/modules/Text/Diff/FormattedHTML/diff.png

}


sa:
  → development/languages/Perl/modules/index[Perl modules]

  → Linux/shell/commands/diff

